[
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607664",
        "quote": "I have always made a distinction between healing and curing. To me, 'healed' represents a condition of one's life; 'cured' relates strictly to one's physical condition. In other words, there may be healed quadriplegics and AIDS patients, and cured cancer patients who are leading unhealthy lives.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607664"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Distinction",
                "url": "/topics/distinction"
            },
            {
                "name": "Other",
                "url": "/topics/other"
            },
            {
                "name": "Relates",
                "url": "/topics/relates"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607665",
        "quote": "Patients want to be seen as people. For me, the person's life comes first; the disease is simply one aspect of it, which I can guide my patients to use as a redirection in their lives. When doctors look at their patients, however, they are trained to see only the disease.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607665"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "However",
                "url": "/topics/however"
            },
            {
                "name": "Trained",
                "url": "/topics/trained"
            },
            {
                "name": "One Aspect",
                "url": "/topics/one_aspect"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607666",
        "quote": "The doctor I would want for myself or for anyone else I cared about would be one who understands that disease is more than just a clinical entity; it is an experience and a metaphor, with a message that must be listened to.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607666"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Want",
                "url": "/topics/want"
            },
            {
                "name": "Disease",
                "url": "/topics/disease"
            },
            {
                "name": "More",
                "url": "/topics/more"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607619",
        "quote": "God wants us to know that life is a series of beginnings, not endings. Just as graduations are not terminations, but commencements. Creation is an ongoing process, and when we create a perfect world where love and compassion are shared by all, suffering will cease.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607619"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Graduation",
                "url": "/topics/graduation"
            },
            {
                "name": "Shared",
                "url": "/topics/shared"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607663",
        "quote": "Feelings aroused by the touch of someone's hand, the sound of music, the smell of a flower, a beautiful sunset, a work of art, love, laughter, hope and faith - all work on both the unconscious and the conscious aspects of the self, and they have physiological consequences as well.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607663"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Sound",
                "url": "/topics/sound"
            },
            {
                "name": "Sound Of Music",
                "url": "/topics/sound_of_music"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607637",
        "quote": "Most of us never stop to consider our blessings; rather, we spend the day only thinking about our problems. But since you have to be alive to have problems, be grateful for the opportunity to have them.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607637"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Grateful",
                "url": "/topics/grateful"
            },
            {
                "name": "Alive",
                "url": "/topics/alive"
            },
            {
                "name": "Rather",
                "url": "/topics/rather"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607651",
        "quote": "Inspiration is the greatest gift because it opens your life to many new possibilities. Each day becomes more meaningful, and your life is enhanced when your actions are guided by what inspires you.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607651"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Gift",
                "url": "/topics/gift"
            },
            {
                "name": "Possibilities",
                "url": "/topics/possibilities"
            },
            {
                "name": "Your",
                "url": "/topics/your"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607615",
        "quote": "Being a survivor doesn't mean being strong - it's telling people when you need a meal or a ride, company, whatever. It's paying attention to heart wisdom, feelings, not living a role, but having a unique, authentic life, having something to contribute, finding time to love and laugh. All these things are qualities of survivors.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607615"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Strong",
                "url": "/topics/strong"
            },
            {
                "name": "Telling",
                "url": "/topics/telling"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607643",
        "quote": "Love and peace of mind do protect us. They allow us to overcome the problems that life hands us. They teach us to survive... to live now... to have the courage to confront each day.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607643"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Mind",
                "url": "/topics/mind"
            },
            {
                "name": "Allow",
                "url": "/topics/allow"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607639",
        "quote": "If we had no hope - for a cure, for winning the lottery, for falling in love, for the end of war, for being free of abuse, or for having food, warmth, clothing, and shelter - we would have no reason to go on. What you hope for doesn't matter, but rather the essence of hope itself.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607639"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Reason",
                "url": "/topics/reason"
            },
            {
                "name": "Abuse",
                "url": "/topics/abuse"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607653",
        "quote": "When your heart speaks to you about what you need to do to sustain life on this planet, listen to it, make a difference, and be an inspiration for generations to come. Be inspired by people like Gandhi, Mother Teresa, Rosa Parks, Martin Luther King, Christopher Reeve, Albert Schweitzer, Helen Keller, and many others.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607653"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Generations",
                "url": "/topics/generations"
            },
            {
                "name": "Martin Luther",
                "url": "/topics/martin_luther"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607646",
        "quote": "We participate and are responsible for a lot of the things that happen to us. If you hate your job, you are much more likely to get sick and die at a younger age than someone who's happy at work and has a nice family life and is mentally well adjusted.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607646"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Happy",
                "url": "/topics/happy"
            },
            {
                "name": "Die",
                "url": "/topics/die"
            },
            {
                "name": "Your",
                "url": "/topics/your"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607652",
        "quote": "True inspiration overrides all fears. When you are inspired, you enter a trance state and can accomplish things that you may never have felt capable of doing.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607652"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "May",
                "url": "/topics/may"
            },
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
            },
            {
                "name": "Felt",
                "url": "/topics/felt"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607658",
        "quote": "A surgeon is surrounded by people who are sick, discouraged, afraid, embittered, dying - but also courageous, loving, wise, compassionate and alive.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607658"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Surgeon",
                "url": "/topics/surgeon"
            },
            {
                "name": "Alive",
                "url": "/topics/alive"
            },
            {
                "name": "Surrounded",
                "url": "/topics/surrounded"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607661",
        "quote": "The mind and body are not separate units, but one integrated system. How we act and what we think, eat, and feel are all related to our health. Physicians should be capable of teaching this behavior to patients.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607661"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Mind",
                "url": "/topics/mind"
            },
            {
                "name": "Think",
                "url": "/topics/think"
            },
            {
                "name": "Separate",
                "url": "/topics/separate"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607638",
        "quote": "When my body gets to the point where I can no longer function or feel gratitude, then I'll leave it and become grateful again. But until then, I will appreciate what I have and not whine about what I don't have. I will feel blessed by life and the opportunity to help others see that they are blessed, too.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607638"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Body",
                "url": "/topics/body"
            },
            {
                "name": "Feel",
                "url": "/topics/feel"
            },
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607617",
        "quote": "The question is not, will there be difficulties and threats to our existence, but how will we deal with them and what can we learn from them. How can they become blessings to society, as a life threatening disease is to an individual, by teaching us about the meaning of our life and existence?",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607617"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Deal",
                "url": "/topics/deal"
            },
            {
                "name": "Question",
                "url": "/topics/question"
            },
            {
                "name": "Disease",
                "url": "/topics/disease"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607613",
        "quote": "The spiritual message is we lose our lives in pleasing others; if you're the good child who pleases Mommy and Daddy but internalizes anger, you're setting yourself up for disease.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607613"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Disease",
                "url": "/topics/disease"
            },
            {
                "name": "Mommy",
                "url": "/topics/mommy"
            },
            {
                "name": "Lives",
                "url": "/topics/lives"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607618",
        "quote": "If God had made a perfect world, it would be a magic trick, not creation, with no meaning or place for us to learn and create. Mankind is not yet ready for a perfect world. We do not know how to appreciate perfection.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607618"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Magic",
                "url": "/topics/magic"
            },
            {
                "name": "Perfect",
                "url": "/topics/perfect"
            },
            {
                "name": "Mankind",
                "url": "/topics/mankind"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607616",
        "quote": "I know patients who bring a dozen roses to the doctor's office. And, boy, the next visit, nobody forgets that. You come in and hey - 'Here's the lady who brought the roses' vs. 'Here's the lung cancer.'",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607616"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Next",
                "url": "/topics/next"
            },
            {
                "name": "Here",
                "url": "/topics/here"
            },
            {
                "name": "Brought",
                "url": "/topics/brought"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607645",
        "quote": "Part of my evolution has been to learn how painful most people's childhoods are. They grow up not liking themselves, not loving themselves. Ask people if they were lovable the minute they were born, and watch them sit back and have to think about it. One lady said, 'I suppose so.' That's painful.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607645"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            },
            {
                "name": "Part",
                "url": "/topics/part"
            },
            {
                "name": "Been",
                "url": "/topics/been"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607648",
        "quote": "What I try to get physically healthy people to understand is that they're going to die someday. There is no way out. And dying isn't failure, but not living is, so make use of your time. Don't keeping waiting.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607648"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Waiting",
                "url": "/topics/waiting"
            },
            {
                "name": "Die",
                "url": "/topics/die"
            },
            {
                "name": "Use",
                "url": "/topics/use"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607641",
        "quote": "Life is a miracle, and we need to not fear trying to achieve our potential and reveal the remarkable creation we and all living things are and that our Creator has built into us the ability to induce self-healing.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607641"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Living",
                "url": "/topics/living"
            },
            {
                "name": "Creator",
                "url": "/topics/creator"
            },
            {
                "name": "Reveal",
                "url": "/topics/reveal"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607628",
        "quote": "Stories change people while statistics give them something to argue about.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607628"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Change",
                "url": "/topics/change"
            },
            {
                "name": "Give",
                "url": "/topics/give"
            },
            {
                "name": "Stories",
                "url": "/topics/stories"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607656",
        "quote": "You can survive tough situations and even turn them to your advantage by acting as if you are the person you want to be. When you act like that person, you can become that person. The hard parts are deciding whom you want to become, being willing to rehearse until you become that person, and forgiving yourself until you do.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607656"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Turn",
                "url": "/topics/turn"
            },
            {
                "name": "Willing",
                "url": "/topics/willing"
            },
            {
                "name": "Your",
                "url": "/topics/your"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607627",
        "quote": "Give someone who has faith in you a placebo and call it a hair growing pill, anti-nausea pill or whatever, and you will be amazed at how many respond to your therapy.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607627"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Give",
                "url": "/topics/give"
            },
            {
                "name": "Therapy",
                "url": "/topics/therapy"
            },
            {
                "name": "Will",
                "url": "/topics/will"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607650",
        "quote": "You can't control the world, but when you control your thoughts, you bring order.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607650"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "World",
                "url": "/topics/world"
            },
            {
                "name": "Thoughts",
                "url": "/topics/thoughts"
            },
            {
                "name": "Bring",
                "url": "/topics/bring"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607631",
        "quote": "Your body loves you, but if you do not love your life, it will end it far sooner, thinking it is doing you a favor.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607631"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Love",
                "url": "/topics/love"
            },
            {
                "name": "Doing",
                "url": "/topics/doing"
            },
            {
                "name": "Will",
                "url": "/topics/will"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607657",
        "quote": "I decided to become a surgeon named Bernie who writes books and gives seminars to teach people what he has learned and is still learning about how to deal with life's difficulties.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607657"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Deal",
                "url": "/topics/deal"
            },
            {
                "name": "Still",
                "url": "/topics/still"
            },
            {
                "name": "Named",
                "url": "/topics/named"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607655",
        "quote": "One of the best ways to change is to act as if you are the person you want to become. When you behave as if you are a different person, you change on a very basic level - even your physiology changes. When actors and actresses perform, their body chemistry is altered by the roles they play.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607655"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Play",
                "url": "/topics/play"
            },
            {
                "name": "Roles",
                "url": "/topics/roles"
            },
            {
                "name": "Very",
                "url": "/topics/very"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607660",
        "quote": "An awareness of one's mortality can lead you to wake up and live an authentic, meaningful life.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607660"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Awareness",
                "url": "/topics/awareness"
            },
            {
                "name": "Mortality",
                "url": "/topics/mortality"
            },
            {
                "name": "Wake",
                "url": "/topics/wake"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607634",
        "quote": "I truly feel the best doctors are ones who are criticized by nurses, patients and family. They do not make excuses and learn from their mistakes.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607634"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Learn",
                "url": "/topics/learn"
            },
            {
                "name": "Feel",
                "url": "/topics/feel"
            },
            {
                "name": "Patients",
                "url": "/topics/patients"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607662",
        "quote": "Physicians need to be good technicians and know how to prescribe, but for healing to occur they also need to incorporate philosophy and spirituality into their treatment. We need to feel as well as think.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607662"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Think",
                "url": "/topics/think"
            },
            {
                "name": "Need",
                "url": "/topics/need"
            },
            {
                "name": "Treatment",
                "url": "/topics/treatment"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607622",
        "quote": "If you think about evolution, sleep, at some time, was a dangerous undertaking. You lie down in your cave or shelter, and along comes a predator and has you for dinner. Many creatures do not sleep or sleep while standing so they can escape from dangerous situations.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607622"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Shelter",
                "url": "/topics/shelter"
            },
            {
                "name": "About",
                "url": "/topics/about"
            },
            {
                "name": "Some",
                "url": "/topics/some"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607640",
        "quote": "I see people who die a few minutes after a doctor tells them there is no hope of a cure. They give up and go. Others get angry and find joy in proving the doctor wrong. Something within them is challenged and hopeful. Hope is the divine motivator.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607640"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Die",
                "url": "/topics/die"
            },
            {
                "name": "I See",
                "url": "/topics/i_see"
            },
            {
                "name": "Hopeful",
                "url": "/topics/hopeful"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607629",
        "quote": "Society should see parenting as a public health issue and help parents to bring their children up feeling loved. We have birthing classes, but no parenting classes. The latter is desperately needed if we are to avoid self-destruction.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607629"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Bring",
                "url": "/topics/bring"
            },
            {
                "name": "Needed",
                "url": "/topics/needed"
            },
            {
                "name": "Classes",
                "url": "/topics/classes"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607636",
        "quote": "I have learned to become not an M.D. but a 'C.D.' for the wounded people I meet. Yes, a 'Chosen Dad' who may not like their behavior but loves and reparents them and helps them to heal their lives and find self-worth and self-esteem and save their lives.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607636"
        },
        "topics": [
