                "name": "Communicate",
                "url": "/topics/communicate"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607626",
        "quote": "Parents, teachers, clergy and physicians change lives with their words. It is hypnotic for a child or patient to hear an authority figure's words. As I am always sharing, 'wordswordswords' can become 'swordswordswords,' and we can kill or cure with either words or swords.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607626"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Cure",
