                "url": "/topics/either"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607630",
        "quote": "I was called a 'CD' by a suicidal teenager, who is alive today because I became her 'Chosen Dad,' who loved her. We all have the potential to re-parent ourselves and others.",
