    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607635",
        "quote": "When one teenager dying of cystic fibrosis asked me, 'Why am I different?' I answered, 'Tony, because it makes you beautiful.' He loved my answer because he knew full well how much he had done for the world and that he would be immortal through his love and the fund raising of those who knew him hoping to find a cure for cystic fibrosis.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Bernie Siegel",
            "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607635"
