            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/bernie_siegel_607642",
        "quote": "There is survival behavior, and doctors need to learn from patients who do not die when they are supposed to, instead of saying, 'You're doing very well, so keep doing whatever you are doing.' They should be asking what their patient is doing and pass the information to other patients.",
